{"tid":808871,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇聞] 點解仲有咁多人去金太郎食嘢嘅？","createTime":"2018-09-06T16:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T20:07:40.000Z","uid":121711,"like":38,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"57680aef2930abaceb4456f862b11c501068e37e","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"頭先大約十點幾，我行過深水埗嗰間金太郎，心諗：呢間餐廳仲未執架咩？好奇之下我就隔住個櫥窗玻璃望入去，間餐廳入面竟然坐滿食客！我心諗：見鬼呀？ 今日係七月十四？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢間垃圾餐廳，竟然仲有咁多人去? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢間所謂日本餐廳，我早幾年前食過，係<br />\n賣得好平，但賣果啲所謂壽司根本就係屎嚟，狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家仲去幫襯嘅食客，究竟係咩心態？唔通佢哋既味覺有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ec3732c9119668ef3d0d17cb3d7f62d77a38d7","tid":808871,"uid":195590,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"十點啦<br />\n爭鮮都關門了<br />\n同埋最緊要夠平<br />\n有好多人唔係想品嚐美食<br />\n而只係要維持生命"},{"pid":"5b87f5947c61cf26fc3c7a084fd356ae81d6d3e5","tid":808871,"uid":2572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"熟食可接受"},{"pid":"95efa90db61e2a47c45c81cad74af35332c27851","tid":808871,"uid":73004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"生野真係唔好食<br />\n試過食到腸胃炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71aae01bc812dcc1a3e1e373a079b5c9122f3d8","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ec3732c9119668ef3d0d17cb3d7f62d77a38d7","tid":808871,"uid":195590,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"十點啦<br />\n爭鮮都關門了<br />\n同埋最緊要夠平<br />\n有好多人唔係想品嚐美食<br />\n而只係要維持生命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"咁樣算唔算係深水埗人嘅悲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d0e2839bc0691a9ea341ed4c11023fbc6e78cc","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b87f5947c61cf26fc3c7a084fd356ae81d6d3e5","tid":808871,"uid":2572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"熟食可接受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"你認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa9977cc3e97358013d14bfa644f26543b14987","tid":808871,"uid":195590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71aae01bc812dcc1a3e1e373a079b5c9122f3d8","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ec3732c9119668ef3d0d17cb3d7f62d77a38d7","tid":808871,"uid":195590,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"十點啦<br />\n爭鮮都關門了<br />\n同埋最緊要夠平<br />\n有好多人唔係想品嚐美食<br />\n而只係要維持生命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"咁樣算唔算係深水埗人嘅悲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba0e7d2c3fbbf67973693c50810c8298467f40c","tid":808871,"uid":36242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"本人對食無乜要求<br />\n<br />\n但呢間野真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a7788abc4ff2288e981dbdbab9a28f54cef0c9","tid":808871,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"想食日本野又冇錢<br />\n冇計啦"},{"pid":"5b5dbec8bcf015e69bfbdd7f48b90407873eba89","tid":808871,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"大約一年前真係變到差到食唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27586278b2b531b9bdb1a1ea6f5964b2c3f63117","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:59:26.000Z","msg":"印像中佢哋啲壽司，舊飯一夾就散，而塊刺身係從來冇黐埋過舊飯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知個壽司師傅d手工要差成點先可以將舊壽司整都咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而佢地d刺身拼盤，塊塊d顏色都好暗淡，總之就係好唔新鮮嗰啲顏色，一見到就唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c464452e3ae6a1d969c72e01583307262f97326","tid":808871,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"N年前第一次食海膽就係金太郎食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以海膽比我開頭嘅感覺係：好撚腥好撚臭"},{"pid":"9713379bf151ec6d7beb07cdd5a2bab1b4329726","tid":808871,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"呢間仲劣過明將<br />\n明將都仲有壽司嘅形狀<br />\n呢間係一篤飯上面放件配料"},{"pid":"78ef47b4ee7ec9e4c925d0e46f56e2d721adcbac","tid":808871,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"金太郎食熟野架嘛"},{"pid":"ce42565b75adf49b7678462e530d8943356149e0","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9713379bf151ec6d7beb07cdd5a2bab1b4329726","tid":808871,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"呢間仲劣過明將<br />\n明將都仲有壽司嘅形狀<br />\n呢間係一篤飯上面放件配料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾餐廳，到呢家都仲生存到，佢算唔算係計明將之後另一個香港飲食業嘅傳奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c57fbef0cf704f7e71a6122fd3587ad2307f35c","tid":808871,"uid":150912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"生野一定唔會食<br />\n凍飲都唔會飲,因為永遠有洗潔精味<br />\n以前間唔中貪平會去下,叫個頹拉面/飯<br />\n<br />\n直至有次食食下有隻一半手掌大的超長肥甲由係燈到趺左落台面,D人已經嚇到四散<br />\n然後有個D姐姐行埋去徒手拍撚死佢<br />\n佢抹下手後繼續若無其事捧餐<br />\n自此之後依世都唔會再食金太郎(利申:深水埗果間)"},{"pid":"9cbb66553f64e5d00cba5e108d35c345ac0f7960","tid":808871,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"幫手清理低端人口"},{"pid":"71ad0bedf5f84205af8a2521378ebc4b8ddd6043","tid":808871,"uid":90504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"呢間真係屎食中既極品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇openrice啲食家好評真係笑撚死"},{"pid":"386e4126f0f0724f131f7830e284aea54527d1b0","tid":808871,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa9977cc3e97358013d14bfa644f26543b14987","tid":808871,"uid":195590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71aae01bc812dcc1a3e1e373a079b5c9122f3d8","tid":808871,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ec3732c9119668ef3d0d17cb3d7f62d77a38d7","tid":808871,"uid":195590,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"十點啦<br />\n爭鮮都關門了<br />\n同埋最緊要夠平<br />\n有好多人唔係想品嚐美食<br />\n而只係要維持生命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"咁樣算唔算係深水埗人嘅悲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"住得果度就只係維持生命架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0985a4cb4e10de08399119fd4e725dd0c816a3","tid":808871,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"其實啲野真係食得，同埋含菌量喺合理範圍咪算囉，要求多多，真別扭"},{"pid":"031fb7e7fbc6f80215ca4941468c7b489b57b211","tid":808871,"uid":71524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"好幾年冇去食<br />\n對上一次食到我腸胃炎入埋醫院"},{"pid":"e1543c94956df1d50e5a37ae81bddf88f2ad8a7c","tid":808871,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"我初中得幾十蚊零用 想食日本嘢就係食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5a76b70fc2c9568618fb85448cbf39eb2fc1ff","tid":808871,"uid":28786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦，係你先當佢係壽司鋪，之前成日去食熟野，因為佢係茶記價錢，但起碼有新鮮感過茶記，d野食唔會好似茶記咁一式一樣又油又閪又污穢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3fe451c83058a87d98c9d19435ef8035cef99c","tid":808871,"uid":28786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:12:35.000Z","msg":"入面有煎三文魚扒，比目魚扒，炒牛柳，燒三文魚骨，燒三文魚頭，全部50蚊有找，茶記又冇得食"},{"pid":"01121e4a841116fd5764173e2181ac51b1fe0a87","tid":808871,"uid":91673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"都要有一班人食返d垃圾 先顯其他野高貴"}]}